net.proteusframework.form

Class FormDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.hibernate.dao.DAOHelper
      • net.proteusframework.form.FormDAO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InitializingBean

    @Repository(value="FormDAO")
public class FormDAO
extends net.proteusframework.core.hibernate.dao.DAOHelper
    DAO for form objects. To retrieve form objects, get a QLBuilder, modify it as needed (adding joins and constraints, etc.), then pass it back to the DAO to get the object(s). When modifying the QLBuilder, reference only Hibernate properties that are publicly documented in the API.
    Author:
    Jonathan Crosmer (jcrosmer@i2rd.com)
